forcing himself on her!

191
00:11:03,583 --> 00:11:05,583
Someone stop that girl;
she shouldn't be up there!

192
00:11:05,666 --> 00:11:06,958
[YUZU]
Number two!

193
00:11:07,041 --> 00:11:08,791
